###
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/names/get_names
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "category": "宠物名",
  "length": "两字",
  "gender": "不限",
  "other": "是一只非常调皮的金毛犬，毛发金黄，希望名字听起来活泼可爱"
}

###
